      <title>耶伦警告金融系统仍面临商业房地产和加密货币风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/yellen-warns-financial-system-still-faces-office-space-crypto-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦周五表示，尽管通胀降温和低失业率提振了整体经济，但美国金融体系在 2024 年仍将继续面临商业房地产风险和数字资产带来的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/yellen-warns-financial-system-still-faces-office-space-crypto-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 16:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Janus Henderson 首席执行官谈市场机遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/janus-henderson-ceo-on-market-opportunities-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Janus Henderson 一直在快速增长。随着客户开始转移投资，该公司最近收购了私人信贷管理公司 Victory Park Capital Advisors，并推出了一系列新的 ETF。首席执行官 Ali Dibadj 参加了彭博公开收益节目，谈论了扩张事宜。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/janus-henderson-ceo-on-market-opportunities-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 16:47:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
